1893:The seam-detection layer is where most of the engineering value of a coordination assistant lives. The LLM is the interface; the deterministic rules and heuristic models are the substance. Investment in seam-detection-rule development with named clinical-leadership ownership per rule is multi-quarter work and continues alongside the engineering work.
1897:## Step 4: Receive the Conversation Turn with Input Safety, Identity, and Coordination-Context Loading
